Kaitesi Usta ni umuyobozi w'urwego rw'igihugu rw'imiyoborere (RGB) mu [[Rwanda]].<ref name=":0">https://www.rgb.rw/1/about-rgb/senior-manager</ref> 

== Amashuri yize ==
Kaitesi Usta afite impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga mu mategeko yakuyi muri kaminuza ya Utrecht mu [[Ubuholandi|Buholande]], afite kandi impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya gatatu cya kaminuza mubijyanye n'amategeko yakuye muri kaminuza ya Ottawa muri [[Kanada]], afite n'impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza mu mategeko yakuye muri [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|kaminuza y'u Rwanda.]]<ref name=":0" />

== Umwuga ==
Kaitesi Usta yabaye umwarimu muri kaminuza y'u Rwanda i Huye, yabaye umuyobozi wa  koleji y'ubugeni n'ubumenyi rusange , yabaye umwe mu bakomiseri barindwi bari bagize Komisiyo Ishinzwe gufasha Inteko Ishinga Amategeko kuvugurura Itegeko Nshinga.<ref name=":0" /> <ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/hashyizweho-abayobozi-bakuru-bashya-muri-rgb-na-rbc</ref>

